{"tid":2421832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬依家一粒巨星都冇，仲做乜撚野皇馬呀，執柒咗佢啦！","createTime":"2021-02-24T20:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T06:25:48.000Z","uid":284284,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"83f140deece125d7ba762abbc530ba2329a8bbba","tid":2421832,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T20:56:16.000Z","msg":"由魯爾年代開始皇馬嘅吸引力就係睇佢嘅 A-list 足球明星, 六條煙, Galaticos<br />\n<br />\n但依家嘅皇馬，唔好講話已經冇咗 Raul, Ronaldo, Zidane, CR7 呢種焦點核心巨星<br />\n<br />\n佢連外圍嗰d配角球星都係CR7前朝代30歲+嘅人，真係眼冤<br />\n你既然要用CR7朝代嘅人, 當初就唔好賣CR7啦<br />\n你要賣CR7, 好心就大換血啦, 個個唔賣，賣咗最核心嗰個CR7 (仲有 Bale) ，真係眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比著以前嘅皇馬，前中後三路已經一早收購咗: <br />\nNeymar, Mbappe, Haaland, <br />\nDe Bruyne, Pogba, <br />\nVan Dijk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c307d992af25bfe8c2d784aee927cda2b1f3b9","tid":2421832,"uid":170521,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"有個過氣世三,同MMA之王拉莫斯"},{"pid":"887049056edd1e4e836faca241f89d0509a320a2","tid":2421832,"uid":11512,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7c307d992af25bfe8c2d784aee927cda2b1f3b9","tid":2421832,"uid":170521,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"有個過氣世三,同MMA之王拉莫斯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"而家BALE起熱刺表現完勝世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b040f6afc79248ebb787c74a9eb77595c68eb5","tid":2421832,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"887049056edd1e4e836faca241f89d0509a320a2","tid":2421832,"uid":11512,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7c307d992af25bfe8c2d784aee927cda2b1f3b9","tid":2421832,"uid":170521,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"有個過氣世三,同MMA之王拉莫斯"},"citedBy"